Applications can be submitted for the higher education scholarships disbursed by the Kerala State Higher Education Council (KSHEC) for the year 2016-17. A press note issued here on Tuesday said students from Kerala in the third year of the degree course in government/aided arts and science colleges or university departments (2013-14 admission) can apply for second renewal and students from Kerala in the second year of the degree programme can apply for first renewal. Applications can be submitted online from January 7. The printout of the application form should be submitted to the college principal before January 27. The principals after vetting the forms should forward them to the Council office before February 6. Details can be had from the websitewww.kshec.kerala.gov.in, the press note added.â€” Special Correspondent